OL,3,CWelsh fire services appoint
OL,4,Cindependent body to carry out cultural
OL,5,Creviews
OL,7,FMid and West Wales and North Wales
OL,8,FFire have announced they have
OL,9,Fappointed an independent body to
OL,10,Foversee cultural reviews of the
OL,11,Fservices.
OL,13,FThe two services were ordered by the
OL,14,FWelsh Government to carry out
OL,15,Finvestigations into their cultures
OL,16,Fearlier this year.
OL,18,FThey both say they acknowledge the
OL,19,Fimportance of "fostering a positive
OL,20,Fand supportive workplace".
