OL,3,CWelsh fire services appoint
OL,4,Cindependent body to carry out cultural
OL,5,Creviews
OL,7,FHowever, the union representing
OL,8,Ffirefighters has expressed concern
OL,9,Fthat the reviews will not be robust
OL,10,Fenough.
OL,12,FThe Fire Brigades Union (FBU) has
OL,13,Fcalled for them to be the same as the
OL,14,Finquiry into South Wales Fire, which
OL,15,Funcovered a culture of racism and
OL,16,Fsexism.
OL,18,FIn March, the Welsh Government
OL,19,Fannounced an independent review into
OL,20,Fthe culture at both North and Mid and
OL,21,FWest Wales Fire and Rescue Services.
