OL,3,CWelsh fire services appoint
OL,4,Cindependent body to carry out cultural
OL,5,Creviews
OL,7,FIt followed an ITV Wales investigation
OL,8,Finto the culture of the service in
OL,9,Fnorth Wales, which heard from more
OL,10,Fthan 35 whistleblowers.
OL,12,FAnnouncing the review, the minister in
OL,13,Fcharge of the fire services, Hannah
OL,14,FBlythyn MS also said she had "received
OL,15,Fcorrespondence from current and former
OL,16,Femployees of both organisations,
OL,17,Fincluding allegations of bullying,
OL,18,Fsexual harassment and favouritism in
OL,19,Fpromotion".
