OL,3,CWelsh fire services appoint
OL,4,Cindependent body to carry out cultural
OL,5,Creviews
OL,7,FConfirming the appointment of an
OL,8,Fexternal body to carry out the
OL,9,Freviews, both fire services said they
OL,10,Fhave "jointly appointed Crest Advisory
OL,11,Fto facilitate an independent cultural
OL,12,Freview."
OL,14,FThe FBU has hit out at the
OL,15,Fannouncement; Cerith Griffiths, the
OL,16,Fexecutive member for Wales, said, "The
OL,17,Ffire services are actually reviewing
OL,18,Ftheir 'cultural journeys', not their
OL,19,Fculture".
