OL,3,CWelsh fire services appoint
OL,4,Cindependent body to carry out cultural
OL,5,Creviews
OL,7,F"What happened in South Wales isn't
OL,8,Funique", he said. Mr Griffiths added
OL,9,Fhe thinks the culture at fire services
OL,10,Fhas to be tackled head on, and the
OL,11,Fcurrent proposals mean people won't be
OL,12,Fheard.
OL,14,FChief Fire Officer Dawn Docx at North
OL,15,FWales Fire said she welcomed an
OL,16,Fopportunity "to review how they are
OL,17,Fprogressing on their cultural
OL,18,Fjourneys".
