OL,3,CWelsh fire services appoint
OL,4,Cindependent body to carry out cultural
OL,5,Creviews
OL,7,FAdding, "We first embarked on a
OL,8,Fcultural journey in 2021 with a
OL,9,Fcomprehensive Fire Family Staff Survey
OL,10,Fcommissioned from an independent
OL,11,Fcompany, followed by diligent action
OL,12,Fplans and regular progress updates."
OL,14,FMid and West Wales Fire chief, Roger
OL,15,FThomas, said, "We understand the need
OL,16,Fto seek external validation and input
OL,17,Fto ensure that we continue on the
OL,18,Fright path."
